~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
|											|
|	MFITS 2.0 - Statistical Analyses for X-ray Burst Simulations			|
|	     Marina Wahl, Stony Brook University & LANL, 2013-14			|	
|											|
|											|
|	This package is used to calculates 5 distinct fits on the data			|
|	generated from the X-ray atmosphere simulations.					|
|											|
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


**************************
* INSTRUCTIONS TO RUN IT *
**************************

1) The data to be analyzed should be inside /data/ folder.
2) The names/paths for the above data should be changed into the constant files: /src/constants.py
3) Run /src/main.py
4) You should get the outputs under the folder /output/ and a log file under /logs/


